索。字节跳动安全研究团队基于Ｊｅｄｄａｋ的大量应用实践，总结出隐私计算基础建设的三个关键问题：技术突破、产品创新、领域洞察，以下简要介绍Ｊｅｄｄａｋ　Ｔｅａｍ的相关工作。　·技术突破　：核心是解决隐私计算的能效问题。例如此次ｉＤＡＳＨ竞赛，不但要求分析建模精准安全、而且对计算能效也提出很高要求。尤其是后者，被认为是隐私计算大规模应用和","sup_num":"4","sup_passage":"近日,2023 iDASH 国际隐私计算竞赛落下帷幕,字节跳动安全研究- Jeddak 可信隐私计算团队联合南京大学､南方科技大学､香港城市大学组建的 Jeddak Team 联合战队, 获得机密计算赛道第一名､同态加密赛道第二名的优异成绩 ｡值得一提的是,在iDASH 2022大赛上, Jeddak team 首次参加大赛,即入围可信计算和区块链赛道前三｡ ","sup_passage_score":0.3483591,"sup_source":"中关村在线","sup_title":"字节跳动Jeddak Team在iDASH 2023隐私计算大赛上获得优异成绩_业界资讯-中关村在线","sup_url":"https:\/\/news.zol.com.cn\/844\/8443154.html"}],"entityInfos":[],"modelType":"lizhi_rag","retrySource":"hunyuan_produce","deepRag":0,"sessionId":"619d4655-1df6-4b4b-88d6-325fc08ef0fe","shortAnswer":"","source":"hunyuan_online","displayType":"hunyuan","debugModel":"立知在线","videoConfig":null,"imgsInfo":{"allImages":false,"imgList":[],"photoList":[]},"recallQuery":"","answerMd5":"","isYuanbaoApi":false,"yuanbaoLog":{},"defaultLogoName":"元宝","traceId":"","wapEntityResource":{"wap_js":[],"wap_css":[]},"divideAnswerAdsObject":{},"entityAnswerAdsObject":{},"isHitAdsChangeExp":false,"isPcToTop":true}</script><script>requirejs(["//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/utils.f9cf1b43.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_helpers-views-isomorphic.bb9a17fa.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/vendor-crypto-js.c37a9a7d.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/components-common.300a4401.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_helpers-views-csr-logger.f091764a.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_components-ai-search-bar-pc.b83da4ec.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_helpers-views-csr.24b41d1e.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/card-pc-_helpers-views-csr-logger.27dc097b.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_components-more-action.5869eccb.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_helpers-views-csr-business-logic-yuanbao.fade52c2.js","//search.sogoucdn.com/reactfly/static/js/_components-share.0168962c.js","